Package FormFiles

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorWindow
    The error window to be able to show the user the nature of the error and any information about the error
    Main
    This application is for the internal use of *Business Company Name* only Any other purpose of use is not allowed and all code, algorithms, and designs are the property of the developer and companies who are receiving the product The purpose of the application is to help facilitate the scheduling and management of the internal working of the logistics for the company.
    ReportForm
    Class is used to show the user the information stored within the database, output the information into a local file called UserMadeCSV which will add the results of the request for the user's needed information
    ScheduleForm
    The use of this class is to allow the user to be able to add and pull up deliveries within the database and to add the activities to the trucks such as picking up and dropping off orders as well as traveling to the different locations.
